snippet.title: StoryArcana [OLD - New Trailer on Cyomo Channel]
snippet.description:
STORY ARCANA
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1374920/StoryArcana/

StoryArcana is an open-world wizard school RPG with a large focus on mystery solving, exploration, puzzles and a combat system based around intricate spell-casting. You play as Clay Quilt - an ordinary boy transported to another world and enrolled into a year of wizardry studies as part of a 1-year exchange program.

Website: https://storyarcana.net/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StoryArcana
Discord: https://discord.gg/rvnj7RG
